title: Ashley Dust (1994) Rick McCollum Knight Press
description:
Enter a world of metaphysical adventure with the highly arcane necroborg Ashley Dust! When the realm of the dead becomes restless and intrudes on the world of the living, Ashley must struggle to end this dangerous menace before it's too late. Trapped in the world of the dead, she must find familiar spirits who will aid her against the oncoming horde.
